Musio: So, what do you think of the months?

User: I like them! They're a lot of fun.

Musio: What's your favorite month?

User: I think my favorite month is probably December. I like all of the holidays that happen then.

Musio: What about the other months? Do you have any favorites?

User: I like January because it's a new year and everything feels fresh and new. And I like April because it's when my birthday is.

Musio: Do you have any least favorite months?

User: Not really. I don't mind any of them too much. Except maybe February because it's so short.